data.meta_description: Document( 15) - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This biography summarizes details about the Nigerian actor Yul Edochie. It states that he was born in 1982 in Lagos and debuted in 2005 in the film "The Exquires". Some of his most notable films include "Wind of Glory", "The Billionaires", and "Royal Choice". It provides information about his family including his parents Pete and Josephine Edochie. It also notes that he has multiple wives and children. The biography concludes by stating that Yul Edochie has a net worth of approximately $3.1 million as of 2023 from his acting career and business ventures.
